::: GRIDPROJS :::

The gridprojs library is a FORTRAN library containing various tools to
define and utilize information on geographical grid projections.

::: KEY FEATURES :::

+ Transform spectral variable grids (e.g., the NCEP GFS) to
  Gaussian-latitude grids (e.g., the NCEP GSI).

::: DEPENDENCIES :::

+ NCEP Gaussian-latitude calculations (see noaa_routines.f).

::: COMPILING :::

Move to source code directory:

> cd gridprojs

To compile, do:

> make

To install, do:

> make install

